  "description": {
    "lang": "eng",
    "value": "The Zed IDE loads Language Server Protocol (LSP) configurations from the settings.json file located within a project’s .zed subdirectory. A malicious LSP configuration can contain arbitrary shell commands that run on the host system with the privileges of the user running the IDE. This can be triggered when a user opens project file for which there is an LSP entry."
  },
